      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "UNCLE TONY (7) registered another strong performance last start when he battled on bravely to just miss out over 2138m at this track after leading at the bell as the hot favourite. Has to contend with a very wide draw. Meets a similar line up and he can take this out. MAHINDI NZ (4) produced another fine effort last start when she scored an all of the way win over 1780m at Redcliffe, coming in 6 metres ahead of her rivals. Meeting a deeper field this time but having won all of her last three runs is good enough to play a major role. OHOKA DREAM (6) has trialled three times since his last run so expect he is forward enough to stake a strong claim fresh from a layoff. KONNYMARA (2) is next best after a last start second of nine over 1780m at Redcliffe after racing outside the leader at the bell. Gets every chance from a favourable draw to go one better..",
